cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with 3D shape recognition and retrieval using convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves graphics (cs.GR) as it deals with 3D point clouds. The paper proposes a novel approach to feature extraction, which involves synthesis and convolution, making it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of convolutional neural networks, which is a common technique in neural networks (cs.NE).
